<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Leicestershire, England, U.K.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Cast Iron Welding Services is a specialist provider of cast iron welding and repair services, predominantly serving the global marine engine industry. The website lays out all essential information, including the company's services, its work processes, and various case studies, in an attractive and professional format across several pages. A notable feature is the use of high-resolution images to showcase the business's completed projects.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The "Company" page gives users insight into the business's long history of providing high-quality services. The addition of two introductory videos on the home page highlights its welding services and work processes and denotes a feeling of professionalism.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The website's hero video and supplemental work videos could all be more high-quality to ensure an optimal visual experience. According to accessScan, the website is only semi-compliant with assistive technologies.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-cast-iron-welding-3840x5694-20240625.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-cast-iron-welding-3840x5694-20240625.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop website does a good job of capturing the company's industry expertise and its use of informative videos enhances the overall user experience. However, the company's contact number in the top-right corner could be displayed slightly more prominently. On Google's PageSpeed Insights test, the website has fast page loading times and an optimal performance score of 100/100.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-cast-iron-welding-824x7152-20240625.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-cast-iron-welding-824x7152-20240625.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
