height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>Unlike the desktop version, the mobile website does not feature a hero video, which makes the home page less impactful. Some of the more text-heavy pages would benefit from additional images to give the mobile site a more engaging visual appeal. Performance-wise, the website has fast loading times and it scores 92/100 on Google's PageSpeed Insights test.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
