</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://majorwelding.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://majorwelding.com/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Abbotsford, British Columbia, Canada</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Major Welding is a locally recognized company that specializes in mobile welding, shop fabrication, and pipe fitting solutions. The website's hero video and supporting "Welcome" video act as a showcase of the company's services and introduce visitors to its workspace.</p><p>The vibrant color accents allow the website's vital content, including its contact details and customer testimonials, to shine. A notable feature is the site's user portal, which provides clients with access to the company's dispatch system.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
